显示：2021 年我国城镇宠物（犬猫）消费市场规模接近 2500 亿元，同比增长 20.6%。需求最大的宠物市场为：宠物食品，市场规模约 1280 亿元；宠物医疗，市场规模约 730 亿元；宠物用品，市场规模约 320 亿元。（央视财经）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f9e09a4b43145999fc21b236665e72d2_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "154 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/542496429"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I1tbDkdv8g/VlEAMaCDgyODM2ODM4IJzmqJYGMAQ4lwFABHIJNTQyNDk2NDI5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1657436595.3672907", "card_id": "Q_465337782", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 94}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《王者荣耀》中最接近完美的射手应该是谁？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-69fa2a4a85efceb414e7a5cde67b7a81_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "147 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/465337782"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I1tbDkdv8g/VlEAMaCDY1Njg3ODE1II/CpoYGMAU4aEAFcgk0NjUzMzc3ODJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1657436595.3678505", "card_id": "Q_542493194", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 50}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "日本警方以杀人嫌疑将安倍枪击案嫌疑人移交检察院，他可能面临哪些法律责任？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "日本警方以杀人嫌疑将安倍枪击案嫌疑人移交检察院 据日本广播协会（NHK）10 日报道，当地时间 7 月 10 日上午 9 时左右，日本警方将罪名改为杀人嫌疑将 41 岁的山上徹也移交奈良县地方检察院。因枪击日本前首相安倍晋三，山上徹也于 7 月 8 日因涉嫌杀人未遂被捕。（央视新闻） 日本警方以杀人嫌疑将安倍枪击案嫌疑人移交检察院"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-cfe639d1871a730fd70394b58738ca4a_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "114 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhi